[Music] Under a cloak of black
and a pointed witch's hat

01:19:50.388 --> 01:19:54.381
[music] I saw a face that made
a chill run down my spine

01:19:54.459 --> 01:20:01.021
[music] When she looked me in the eye.
She must have hypnotized me

01:20:01.097 --> 01:20:06.728
[music] 'Cause the next thing I remember
I was there. Standing in her lair

01:20:06.802 --> 01:20:08.792
[music] Watching as she stirred

01:20:09.871 --> 01:20:12.465
[music] And then she looked at me.
And she said these words

01:20:12.540 --> 01:20:14.370
[music] Eye of newt and wing of bat

01:20:14.441 --> 01:20:16.739
[music] And a long black whisker
from a big black cat

01:20:16.810 --> 01:20:21.109
[music] Spider legs and wolfhound fur.
Bring it to a boil and begin to stir

01:20:21.180 --> 01:20:23.204
[music] Add poison Ivy with a hemlock root

01:20:23.281 --> 01:20:25.613
[music] And a thread from
the collar of a vampire suit

01:20:25.683 --> 01:20:27.707
[music] Guaranteed with your money back. Too

01:20:27.784 --> 01:20:31.481
[music] But be careful when
you mess with witch's brew
